creator: Calven
descriptionHtml:
Calven is the workplace experience app designed to enable the future of work.

This is a companion app to the Calven platform, and company must have an account set up for Calven.

With Calven you can:
Select your hybrid work preferences, view colleagues availability and locations, schedule and book desks and meeting rooms, browse and book events and drive team coordination.
descriptionShort: The experience platform enabling the future of work
